Stealth Warriors, 57 models broken down into -

Specialist Stealth Warriors, 22 models broken down into -
- 5 Missile Troopers with Rocket Launchers
- 3 Missile Loaders with Laser-Carbines carrying spare rockets
- 5 Flame Troopers with Flame Throwers and petrol tanks
- 4 Medics (2 treating injured troops)
